&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Frontend Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to help us build the next generation of Flo’s platform and user experiences.&lt;br&gt;You’ll work on the foundation that powers interactive surveys and dynamic content inside the Flo app — building SDKs, reusable components, and internal tooling that enable other product teams to deliver exceptional experiences quickly and reliably.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our frontend stack is based on &lt;strong&gt;React&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;TypeScript&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;Next.js&lt;/strong&gt;, with a strong focus on performance, maintainability, and testing.&lt;br&gt;We care deeply about quality: we use TypeScript for type safety, Jest and Playwright for automated testing, and continuously evolve our design system and UI Kit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll be doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
