&lt;li&gt;Refactor and improve existing codebases for performance, reliability, and maintainability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write clean, modular, well-documented code and advocate for engineering best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively participate in the frontend community at Flo, sharing ideas and driving improvements in architecture and development processes.&lt;/li&gt;
