&lt;p&gt;This is a senior IC role with company-wide visibility, partnering with leadership across User Acquisition, Finance, Analytics, and Engineering. It&#39;s equally hands-on in delivery: co-leading the team day-to-day with your engineering manager pair, writing the specs, defining the epics, staying close to the work.&lt;/p&gt;
